nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROB Simple_2comp $INPUT ID TIME AMT DV MDV CMT ADDL II SPECIES SEX MULTIPLE DOSE ROUTE FORMULATION $DATA C:\Users\admin\Documents\GitHub\Autophage\PKTK_dataset_plasma.csv IGNORE=@ IGNORE=(SPECIES.NE.1)
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4
$PK ;---- FIXED EFFECT DEFINITION ---- TVCL = THETA(3) TVV2 = THETA(4) TVV3 = THETA(5) TVQ = THETA(6) TVKA = THETA(7)
;---- RANDOM EFFECT DEFINITION ----
CL = TVCL * EXP(ETA(1)) V2 = TVV2 * EXP(ETA(2)) V3 = TVV3 * EXP(ETA(3)) Q = TVQ * EXP(ETA(4)) KA = TVKA * EXP(ETA(5)) F1 = THETA(8) - THETA(10) * DOSE / (THETA(9) + DOSE) * EXP(ETA(6)) S2 = V2
$ERROR IPRED = F W = SQRT(THETA(1)**2 + THETA(2)**2 * IPRED**2) IRES = DV - IPRED IWRES = IRES / W Y = IPRED + W * EPS(1)
$THETA 0.0001 FIX 0.5 (0, 10, 30) (0, 30, 100) (0, 50, 500) (0, 5, 200) (0, 1.5, 20)
(0, 1) (0, 50) (0, 1) $OMEGA 0.1 0 FIX 0 FIX 0 FIX 0 FIX 0.1 $SIGMA 1 FIX
$ESTIMATION NOABORT MAXEVAL=9999 METHOD=1 INTER PRINT=10 SIGDIGITS=3
$TABLE ID TIME AMT DV MDV IPRED CWRES IWRES ONEHEADER NOPRINT FILE = sdtab005_6 $TABLE ID CL V2 V3 Q KA F1 DOSE ONEHEADER NOPRINT NOAPPEND FILE = patab005_6
